{"tid":228496,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【真相】在沒有Wsapp 的三小時","createTime":"2017-05-04T02:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T05:31:29.000Z","uid":64971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae633af488f5600c3501d884638709c9b12d023f","tid":228496,"uid":64971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"第一節： Hacker<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「Siri, Time」<br />\n<br />\n「Half past three in the morning」<br />\n<br />\n攤坐在電腦桌前，Hacker終於攻破了最後的關口。<br />\n<br />\n「是今晚嗎?」他對著眼前的麥克杯，提出了一條沒有答案的問題。<br />\n<br />\n「思考需要糖分」，這句在Hacker腦中閃過，是他偶像的口頭蟬。<br />\n<br />\n喝光了杯中僅剩的果汁，他決定在最終行動之前，不妨再添一杯。<br />\n<br />\n「呀&hellip;.」他跌坐在電腦椅上，反彈的衝擊更是令背後發痛。<br />\n<br />\n長時間的作業，雙腳似是因坐得太久而發軟，無力支撐這己經瘦弱的身驅。<br />\n<br />\nHacker悶哼了一聲。<br />\n<br />\n「嘖，是要我不能退縮嗎?」 他雙眼注視著眼前雪白的螢幕，默默地將手指移到鍵盤的中央。<br />\n<br />\n「我大概會被捉吧」Hacker 在按下發送鍵的同時，命運的巨輪開始轉動。<br />\n<br />\n聲明：本文為短篇創作。<br />\n作者：兩個怪人。"},{"pid":"d4285301593f9d2cd01d1f0bb7ba43a5e62c612e","tid":228496,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287d418db81cfcec28155b7b962a2e92c49f3452","tid":228496,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389318e1b6d7d11d510469679f480c1fca4b7948","tid":228496,"uid":64971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"第二節： Boss<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nBoss 俯視著窗外，依稀的燈光照著在數小時後將會逼滿上班族的馬路。<br />\n<br />\n他很喜歡這種感覺，或者說，這是Boss 的本性。<br />\n<br />\n兩小時後他會出發到上海，嚴格來說，他應該在別墅中等著老司機的到來，然後由秘書向他匯報未來二四小時會發生的事。<br />\n<br />\n但他沒有這樣做，因為他是BOSS。<br />\n<br />\nBOSS 不喜歡被下屬摸透，秘書要做的是「跟從」，不是「計劃」。所以他回來了，半小時後當秘書發現自己的老闆不在應該出現的地方，他知道自己的手機會響起。但他不會接聽，因為桌上的電話一定會在一分鐘內響起，然後轉到留言。<br />\n<br />\n「留言的聲音能夠傳到這個位置」，BOSS 知道。<br />\n<br />\n想起這個新秘書最後會跑進辦公室，擰開那銀色手柄，看見自己就像如獲至寶的表情，Boss 開始有點興奮。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nBoss，隨手將手機放到沙發，對著黑夜，為那漲起的小兄弟進行了男人的儀式。"},{"pid":"e6a435442ec4e91743d8aa250d8a5386567bb85d","tid":228496,"uid":64971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b303c2693ef40cf6f95e9ba12a059b8b067f472","tid":228496,"uid":77374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"在沒有WhatsApp 的三小時<br />\n<br />\n0訊息<br />\n<br />\n~完~"},{"pid":"cffbfad15f7e927591a0755d9ee33ed5f50fc9dd","tid":228496,"uid":57398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/83y0vrlx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F83y0vrlx&h=075dec83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51adc9e09c1e46d9017bd03fac152def5e4aa8e8","tid":228496,"uid":64971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/83y0vrlx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F83y0vrlx&h=075dec83&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最威係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}